  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kdeadmin</title>

    <para>This package provides several <application>KDE</application> clients 
    useful for managing a system. Clients include programs for managing users, 
    initialization files, cron, and network connections.</para>

    &lfs67_checked;

